Good day! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley in town. My name is Jamie. May I know your name, please?

Hi Jamie, my name is Alex.

Nice to meet you, Alex! How can I assist you regarding your billing today?

I had a question about my recent bill. It seems higher than usual.

I understand. To help you better, could I have your billing account number, please?

Sure, it's one two three four five six.

Thank you, Alex. And could you please confirm the last four digits of the phone number associated with the account?

It's seven eight nine zero.

Great, thank you for providing that information. I will look into your account and give you a detailed explanation regarding the bill discrepancy.

Thanks, Jamie. I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Alex. Thanks for your patience. If you need any further assistance, feel free to call us back. Have a great day!
